汤普森花了五年的时间创作和改写剧本，这一期间她还参加了其他电影的制作<ref name="Stempel" />{{rp|249}}<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|208}}<ref name="Parrill" />{{rp|6}}。汤普森感觉原著的用词“远比（奥斯汀）之后的小说更晦涩难懂”，因此希望可以在简化其中对白的同时保持“原作中的优雅和机智”<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|252}}。她发现在创作剧本的过程中，第一稿通常“有许多好素材”，但还需加以剪辑，而第二稿则“几乎可以肯定是垃圾……因为你会变得惊惶失措”<ref name="Thompson-Doran-1995">{{cite video |year=1995 |title=Audio commentary for ''Sense and Sensibility'' | medium=DVD |publisher=Columbia Pictures |location=Special Features |people=Thompson, Emma; Lindsay Doran}}</ref>{{rp|01:33:00-01:33:25}}。汤普森把自己能够完成这个剧本部分归功于多兰，称她“在那个过程中帮助我，让我成长并加以指导……我是跟在她的脚步后面学会了剧本创作”<ref>{{cite news |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20130921053831/http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/movies/emma-thompson-on-child-rearing-screenwriting-and-acting-260719/ |url=http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/movies/emma-thompson-on-child-rearing-screenwriting-and-acting-260719/ |title=Emma Thompson on child rearing, screenwriting and acting |first=Carrie |last=Rickey |work=The Philadelphia Inquirer |date=2010-08-23 |accessdate=2014-01-27 |archivedate=2013-09-21}}</ref>。

汤普森的第一稿剧本均为手写，长度超过300页，需要缩减<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P3-1308993761.html |title=A sensible screenplay |first=Jim |last=Welsh |work=Literature/Film Quarterly |via=HighBeam Research |date=1996-01-01 |accessdate=2014-01-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140611025654/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P3-1308993761.html |archive-date=2014-06-11 |dead-url=yes }}{{subscription required}}</ref><ref name="EWinterview">{{cite news|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,299930,00.html |title=Emma Thompson: Write for the part |work=Entertainment Weekly |first=Anne |last=Thompson |date=1995-12-15 |accessdate=2014-01-27 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130925121715/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C299930%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-09-25 }}</ref>。她发现有关浪漫情感的内容是最难“兼顾”的<ref name="EWinterview" />，稿件中对威洛比和爱德华两角的描写受到了一些批评，多兰之后回忆称，这些批评主要是指在威洛比出场前，整个故事并没有真正开始，而爱德华的情节则成了侧面描写的背景故事。汤普森和多兰很快意识到，要想让这个剧本得到认可，必须要先花上20分钟的时间让包括爱德华在内于前期就开始出现的人物变得鲜明起来{{sfn|Thompson|Doran|1995|loc=01:33:25-01:33:49}}。于此同时，汤普森也希望避免描绘出“两个女人坐等男人上门”的效果<ref name="Gay">{{cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=JYkMbaYAKMoC&pg=PA90&lpg=PA90&dq=Jane+Austen+on+Screen+penny+gay&source=bl&ots=5ZQ_VwxCFw&sig=lD6h3BkH_5ync7tbeHgos7QIU70&hl=en&sa=X&ei=dHdHUrimBLOLyQH_s4CQBA&ved=0CEgQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Jane%20Austen%20on%20Screen%20penny%20gay&f=false |last=Gay |first=Penny |editor1-first=Gina |editor1-last=MacDonald |editor2-first=Andrew |editor2-last=MacDonald |title=Jane Austen on Screen |publisher=Cambridge University Press |year=2003 |chapter=Sense and Sensibility in a Post-Feminist world: Sisterhood is Still Powerful |isbn=0-521-79325-4 |accessdate=2014-01-27 |archive-date=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627022808/http://books.google.com/books?id=JYkMbaYAKMoC&pg=PA90&lpg=PA90&dq=Jane+Austen+on+Screen+penny+gay&source=bl&ots=5ZQ_VwxCFw&sig=lD6h3BkH_5ync7tbeHgos7QIU70&hl=en&sa=X&ei=dHdHUrimBLOLyQH_s4CQBA&ved=0CEgQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Jane%20Austen%20on%20Screen%20penny%20gay&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{rp|92}}，她逐渐将剧本中达什伍德姐妹间的关系和彼此的爱情故事尽可能放到同等位置上<ref name="tcmfmiller" />。

多兰带着完成的剧本草案向多家制片公司推销以求获得资金，但许多公司都对汤普森作为剧作家的能力持有警惕，当时她还是一位没有什么名气的女演员，之前从未创作过电影剧本。不过，哥伦比亚电影公司高管艾米·帕斯卡（{{lang|en|Amy Pascal}}）对汤普森的参与表示支持，并签约同意担任[[制片人|制片人]]和发行商。<ref name="ctdoran" /><ref name="HuffPostNannyMcPhee" />

==== 李安加入 ====
[[台湾|台湾]]导演李安1993年推出的家庭[[喜剧片|喜剧片]]《喜宴》获得了成功，该片由他亲自编剧、执导并担任制片人。在此以前，他从未参与过奥斯汀小说改编影视作品的制作<ref name="Mills-2009">{{cite book |first=Clifford W. |last=Mills |title=Ang Lee |publisher=Chelsea House Publishers |year=2009 |isbn=1-60413-566-2 |url=http://books.google.com/books/about/Ang_Lee.html?id=jOZB0khbgY4C |accessdate=2014-01-27 |archive-date=2020-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200817125056/https://books.google.com/books/about/Ang_Lee.html?id=jOZB0khbgY4C |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{rp|67}}，但多兰从《喜宴》中看到了李安在社会喜剧背景下驾御家庭复杂关系的能力，觉得这也是奥斯汀小说故事情节所需要的特质<ref name="tcmfmiller">{{cite web|url=http://www.tcm.com/this-month/article/62625%7C0/Sense-and-Sensibility.html |title=Sense and Sensibility |publisher=Turner Classic Movies |first=Frank |last=Miller |accessdate=2014-01-27 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130701174531/http://www.tcm.com/this-month/article/62625%7C0/Sense-and-Sensibility.html |archivedate=2013-07-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。回忆起这个决定她表示，虽然[[英语|英语]]不是李安的第一[[语言|语言]]，但外国导演会给人一种更知性的吸引力<ref name="dailybeastlunch" />。多兰给李安寄了一份汤普森剧本的副本，他对此表示有兴趣，但对自己是否应该接拍也持谨慎态度<ref name="Kerr" />。多兰一共面试了15位导演，但她表示，李安是其中为数不多的几位能够理解奥斯汀幽默感的[[候选人|候选人]]之一，他表示自己想要拍一部“让人们心碎到两个月后还没有完全恢复”的电影<ref name="Kerr">{{cite news |title=Sense and sensitivity |first=Sarah |last=Kerr |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=MuECAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA44&dq=sense+and+sensibility+emma+thompson#v=onepage&q=sense%20and%20sensibility&f=false |work=New York |date=1996-04-01 |accessdate=2014-01-27 |archive-date=2014-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140627022735/http://books.google.com/books?id=MuECAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA44&dq=sense+and+sensibility+emma+thompson#v=onepage&q=sense%20and%20sensibility&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

