《理智与情感》的原定制作周期为58天，最后延长到65天<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|209}}。电影于1995年4月中旬在德文郡多个地点开拍，首先是在萨尔特伦宅第拍摄片中诺兰庄园的镜头<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/travel/2009/jun/07/sense-sensibility-saltram-walking-guide |title=The Sense and Sensibility estate, Saltram House, Devon |work=The Guardian |date=2009-06-07 |accessdate=2014-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140203163838/http://www.theguardian.com/travel/2009/jun/07/sense-sensibility-saltram-walking-guide |archive-date=2014-02-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Higson-2011" />{{rp|149}}，温丝莱特和琼斯在这里拍摄了第一组镜头，即她们的角色首次得知巴顿庄园<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|215, 217-219}}。由于萨尔特伦宅第属[[國家名勝古蹟信託|国家信托]]所有，因此谢玛斯必须在开拍前签署协议，该组织成员也留在片场对拍摄过程仔细加以监督。剧组之后还返回拍摄了多个镜头直到4月29日结束<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|215, 217, 222, 226-227}}。第二个拍摄地点是弗里特大宅（{{lang|en|Flete House}}），这是片中詹宁斯夫人位于伦敦的房产，爱德华和露西首次在这里见到埃莉诺<ref name=Voigts-Virchow-2004>{{cite book |first=Eckart |last=Voigts-Virchow |title=Janespotting and Beyond: British Heritage Retrovisions Since the Mid-1990s |page=11 |chapter="Corset Wars": An Introduction to Syncretic Heritage Film Culture Since the Mid-1990s |publisher=Gunter Narr Verlag Tubingen |editor1-first=Eckart |editor1-last=Voigts-Virchow |year=2004 |isbn=3-8233-6096-5 |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=DwMSx3q9Z4gC&pg=PA9&lpg=PA9&dq=janespotting+and+beyond+syncretic+heritage+film&source=bl&ots=uVTuJXwLMM&sig=t3DOddCEr6KcuRVHlh5BkPj28xE&hl=en&sa=X&ei=pYxHUuq8NuTYyAHQg4GAAQ&ved=0CC4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=janespotting%20and%20beyond%20syncretic%20heritage%20film&f=false |accessdate=2014-01-28 |archive-date=2014-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102062553/http://books.google.com/books?id=DwMSx3q9Z4gC&pg=PA9&lpg=PA9&dq=janespotting+and+beyond+syncretic+heritage+film&source=bl&ots=uVTuJXwLMM&sig=t3DOddCEr6KcuRVHlh5BkPj28xE&hl=en&sa=X&ei=pYxHUuq8NuTYyAHQg4GAAQ&ved=0CC4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=janespotting%20and%20beyond%20syncretic%20heritage%20film&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|224}}。达什伍德夫人和三个女儿搬进的平房则是弗里特大宅的一套石制平房，汤普森称其为“我们所见过的最漂亮景点之一”<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|233}}。

5月份，剧组在[[贝瑞波默罗伊|贝瑞波默罗伊]]（{{lang|en|Berry Pomeroy}}）一间精美的乡间[[教堂|教堂]]拍摄片尾的婚礼镜头<ref>{{cite news |archivedate=2014-01-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140128152230/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/2433499/Weddings-fall-at-Sense-and-Sensibility-church-after-bells-break.html |url= http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/2433499/Weddings-fall-at-Sense-and-Sensibility-church-after-bells-break.html |title=Weddings fall at Sense and Sensibility church after bells break |work=The Daily Telegraph |first=Nick |last=Britten |date=2010-07-18 |accessdate=2014-01-28}}</ref><ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|230}}。5月10日到12日期间拍摄完成了玛丽安初遇威洛比的镜头，由于需要在下雨天到山上拍摄，因此给物流运输上带来了困难<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|235-237}}。李安把这段镜头拍了约50次，众演员都在造雨机器下湿透了，这导致温丝莱特最终因[[过度换气症候群|过度换气]]而晕倒<ref name="Mills-2009" />{{rp|70}}<ref name="Thompson-Doran-1995" />{{rp|6:15-6:25}}。拍摄中途还遇到了其它麻烦，例如温丝莱特就因腿上感染静脉炎而不得不跛行，还有一次从楼梯上摔下而扭伤了手腕<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|261-262}}。

5至7月，剧组在英格兰其它多处国家信托的房产取景。[[威尔特郡|威尔特郡]][[索尔兹伯里|索尔兹伯里]]的[[特拉法加别墅|特拉法加别墅]]（{{lang|en|Trafalgar House}}）和[[威尔顿别墅|威尔顿别墅]]（{{lang|en|Wilton House}}）分别给片中的巴顿庄园和伦敦舞厅取景。同样位于索尔兹伯里，建于18世纪的蒙佩森宅邸（{{lang|en|Mompesson House}}则成了詹宁斯夫人豪华的[[联排别墅|联排别墅]]。位于南萨默塞特（{{lang|en|South Somerset}}），建于16世纪的蒙塔丘特楼在片中作为帕尔默夫妇的克利夫兰大宅<ref name="Thompson-1995" />{{rp|286-287}}。还有一些镜头是在德文郡的康普顿城堡<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111226181442/http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/main/w-global/w-localtoyou/w-devoncornwall/w-devoncornwall-places/w-devoncornwall-places-otherspecialplaces.htm |archivedate=2011-12-26 |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.nationaltrust.org.uk/main/w-global/w-localtoyou/w-devoncornwall/w-devoncornwall-places/w-devoncornwall-places-otherspecialplaces.htm |title=Other special places to visit |publisher=National Trust for Places of Historic Interest or Natural Beauty |accessdate=2011-12-26}}</ref>和[[格林尼治|格林尼治]]的[[英国国家海事博物馆|英国国家海事博物馆]]取景<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/jul/10/3d-film-festival-greenwich-indian |title=This week's new film events |work=The Guardian |first=Steve |last=Rose |date=2010-07-10 |accessdate=2014-01-29 |archivedate=2014-01-28 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140128161508/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2010/jul/10/3d-film-festival-greenwich-indian}}</ref>。

